##### [中等] 1749. 任意子数组和的绝对值的最大值【前缀和】【动态规划】[[前缀和 + 动态规划](https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-absolute-sum-of-any-subarray/solution/1749-ren-yi-zi-shu-zu-he-de-jue-dui-zhi-0gqqh/)] [[1749. 任意子数组和的绝对值的最大值](https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-absolute-sum-of-any-subarray/)]


### 代码

```java
class Solution {
	public int maxAbsoluteSum(int[] nums) {
		long max = Math.max(nums[0], 0);
		long min = Math.min(nums[0], 0);
		long sum = 0;
		long ans = Integer.MIN_VALUE;
		for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {
			sum += nums[i];
			long cur = Math.max(Math.abs(sum - max), Math.abs(sum - min));
			ans = Math.max(cur, ans);
			max = Math.max(max, sum);
			min = Math.min(min, sum);
		}
		return (int) ans;
	}
}
```
